{"word":"προλαμβάνω","slug":"προλαμβάνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<p ><strong><elT>προλαμβάνω</elT></strong> 2 <a href=\"#_ftn1\" name=\"_ftnref1\">aor.</a> <el>προέλαβον</el>; 1 aor. <a href=\"#_ftn2\" name=\"_ftnref2\">pass.</a> <el>προελήμφθην</el> (on the <a href=\"#_ftn3\" name=\"_ftnref3\">sp.</a> s. <a href=\"#_ftn4\" name=\"_ftnref4\">B-D-F</a> §101 p. 53; <a href=\"#_ftn5\" name=\"_ftnref5\">Mlt-H.</a> 246f) (<a href=\"#_ftn6\" name=\"_ftnref6\">Trag.</a>, <a href=\"#_ftn7\" name=\"_ftnref7\">Hdt.</a>+; <a href=\"#_ftn8\" name=\"_ftnref8\">ins</a>, <a href=\"#_ftn9\" name=\"_ftnref9\">pap</a>, <a href=\"#_ftn10\" name=\"_ftnref10\">LXX</a>, <a href=\"#_ftn11\" name=\"_ftnref11\">EpArist</a>; <a href=\"#_ftn12\" name=\"_ftnref12\">SibOr</a> 3, 569; <a href=\"#_ftn13\" name=\"_ftnref13\">Philo</a>, <a href=\"#_ftn14\" name=\"_ftnref14\">Joseph</a>., <a href=\"#_ftn15\" name=\"_ftnref15\">Just</a>.; <a href=\"#_ftn16\" name=\"_ftnref16\">Ath.</a>, R. 25 p. 78, 23) <a href=\"#_ftn17\" name=\"_ftnref17\">prim.</a> ‘take before(hand)’.</p>"}]}